snippet.title: Mind blowing brain teaser - Folding paper to the moon
snippet.description:
Can you solve this mind blowing brain teaser? How many times can you fold a piece a paper before it reaches the moon? Find out the solution in this brain teaser in this video.

My name is Chris and my passion is to teach math. Learning should never be a struggle which is why I make all my videos as simple and fun as possible. I cover all subjects from basic level math through upper level calculus and statistics. I also make brain teaser and Rubik's cube videos for fun. 

Check out all of my other brain teasers.
